This is a hidden file (dot-prefixed) on Unix/macOS systems.

Hidden files are common and important:
- .gitignore, .editorconfig, .env
- .ssh/, .gnupg/, .aws/ (sensitive!)
- .bashrc, .zshrc, .profile
- .DS_Store (excluded)
- .bsignore (BetterSpotlight's own config)

BetterSpotlight should:
1. Index hidden files by default (they contain useful content)
2. Respect exclusion rules for specific hidden files/dirs
3. Mark sensitive hidden directories as metadata-only
4. Handle the dot prefix in filename extraction correctly
